      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_c2b9634b-de89-492c-ba82-47079ab7b56b" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Settings</strong> icon [1]. </p>
<p>To change the status colors, click the <strong>View Options</strong> tab [2] and click the <strong>Edit</strong> icon [4].</p>
  </div>
